title: CAT 390F - 2000 Hour Service
description: Full service including engine oil filter hydraulic filter fuel filter replacement. Undercarriage inspection - track pads at 60% remaining. Swing bearing grease. Coolant flush and refill. All systems operational.

title: Manitowoc 14000 - Wire Rope Replacement
description: Main hoist wire rope failed during annual load test at 110% capacity. Complete replacement of 1200 ft main hoist rope and 800 ft auxiliary rope. New rope run-in procedure completed. Load test passed at 125%.

title: Liebherr LTM 1100 - Annual Certification
description: Annual OSHA/ANSI B30.5 crane inspection. Structural inspection of boom sections and turntable. Load test at 100% and 110% capacity. All safety devices functional. LMI calibrated. Certification renewed through January 2027.

title: Link-Belt TCC-750 - Hydraulic Pump Repair
description: Main hydraulic pump failure causing loss of boom extension and retraction. Pump removed and rebuilt. New seals bearings and pistons installed. System flushed and refilled. Load tested satisfactory.

title: CAT 336 - 1000 Hour Service
description: Engine oil and filter change. Hydraulic system filter replacement. Air filter service. Track tension adjustment. Bucket pin and bushing inspection - wear within limits. Wiper blade replacement.

title: CAT D8T - Undercarriage Rebuild
description: Track chain replacement both sides. New track rollers and idlers. Sprocket rebuild. Total undercarriage overhaul at 8500 hours. Machine down 5 days for work.

title: Kenworth T880 #1 - DOT Annual Inspection
description: Annual DOT safety inspection. Brakes tested and within spec. Lighting and reflectors functional. Frame and suspension inspected. Tires at 70% tread remaining. All DOT stickers current.

title: Kenworth T880 #2 - Transmission Repair
description: Transmission slipping in 4th and 5th gear. Rebuilt Allison 4500 transmission with new clutch packs and torque converter. Road tested 50 miles. All gears shifting properly.

title: Generac 200kW - Load Bank Test
description: Annual load bank testing at 25% 50% 75% and 100% rated capacity. All tests passed. Voltage and frequency regulation within spec. Transfer switch operation verified. Fuel system inspected.

title: JLG 1250AJP - Annual Inspection and Recertification
description: Annual aerial work platform inspection per ANSI A92.5. Structural inspection of boom sections. Hydraulic system pressure tested. Platform leveling verified. Emergency lowering tested. Safety decals updated.

title: Putzmeister 56Z - Boom Cylinder Reseal
description: Hydraulic leak at boom section 3 cylinder. Cylinder removed resealed and reinstalled. Boom operation tested through full range of motion. Concrete delivery system flushed and inspected. Wear plates at 40% remaining.

title: Ford F-550 - 30K Mile Service
description: Oil and filter change. Brake inspection - 50% pad remaining. Tire rotation. Transmission fluid check. Battery tested. Air filter replaced. DEF system checked. All lights and signals functional.

title: Atlas Copco XAS 750 - Air End Rebuild
description: Excessive oil carryover indicating air end seal wear. Complete air end rebuild with new rotors bearings and seals. Oil separator replaced. System tested at rated 750 CFM at 125 PSI.

title: Wirtgen W210Fi - Drum Replacement
description: Milling drum teeth at end of life after Hardy Toll Road project. Complete drum with 180 new carbide teeth installed. Conveyor belt replaced. Water spray system cleaned and tested.

title: Trimble SX12 - Annual Calibration
description: Annual factory calibration and certification. Horizontal and vertical angle accuracy verified. EDM accuracy tested. Autolock and robotic functions tested. Firmware updated to v4.2. Calibration certificate issued.
